These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, electronic
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | electronic |
| Food     | cauliflower | asparagus  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
City: san-francisco, boston
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, dannemann
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| City    | san-francisco      | boston         |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks
2 different pets are kept: bird, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | writing   |
| Pet       | lizard  | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
